  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"245\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKQJkH4a1hjH7o0MSmIdKhmkviaOfz4527JKKKnvpBuyx7h6ezk5k2Rbw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505181355\" data-ratio=\"0.42421875\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f23144f2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKQJkH4a1hjH7o0MSmIdKhmkviaOfz4527JKKKnvpBuyx7h6ezk5k2Rbw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">ICML祭出一套疯狂的评审机制，竟成了学术界的救命稻草。连AI教父Bengio都站台支持：在信息过载的时代，我们必须学会利用「偏见」来降噪。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2025年，NeurIPS的投稿洪峰冲破3万大关——这比一年前直接翻了近乎一倍。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这3万篇论文构成的认知过载，足以让现存的任何人类评审系统当场宕机。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">学术界的「同行评审」系统，名存实亡。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"290\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"542\" data-imgfileid=\"505181424\" data-ratio=\"0.5152091254752852\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1052\" data-width=\"1052\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=45a0c433&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKoTpZedtiaUXMx4Bk2hF5Ns9fsxdfypcVPF9aphf1yny0u7FMGtEzehA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">面对这场审稿危机，ICML 2026终于坐不住了。他们推出了一项极具颠覆性、甚至带有博弈论色彩的新政——作者自评级。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6885245901639344\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"976\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"976\" data-height=\"672\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"387\" data-imgfileid=\"505181425\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=18d89db8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicK6duibLO9ZXYf0TIC0ia3LJVDmKWCA3NYrkUEotrpua7cOrwiaoOKnHriaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们审不动了。你们自己招吧：手里这几张牌，哪张是凑数的废纸，哪张是真正的王炸？</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这听起来像是「让嫌疑人给自己判案」。如此疯狂的政策为什么能落地？因为它背后站着一位真正的神——Yoshua Bengio。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">机制突变：从「猫鼠游戏」到「带枪投案」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">ICML2026的这波操作，表面上是在向作者索要权力，实际上是给了一块「免死金牌」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在过去，同行评审是一场「猫鼠游戏」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">作者是「嫌疑人」，竭尽全力把垃圾包装成金子；评审员是「侦探」，拿着显微镜找破绽。大家互不信任，且互相伤害。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但现在，ICML摊牌了：「侦探不够用了，请嫌疑人协助破案。」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你可能会问：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">让作者自评？那还不全员满分？谁会承认自己写的是垃圾？</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这正是博弈论最精彩的杀招：保序回归。系统不看你打的分数，它只看你的出牌顺序。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你不需要告诉系统这篇论文是9分还是3分，你只需要告诉系统：在我投的这3篇里，A&gt;B&gt;C</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">以前，你可以把3篇平庸的5分论文全吹成9分神作，赌评审员眼瞎放水。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现在，如果你为了捞3分的烂文，硬把它排在9分神作之前，结果烂文没救成，神作的分数还被强行拉低。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为什么ICML敢这么做？因为他们手里有数据。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">ICML 2023的秘密实验结果显示，作者对自己论文的排序，更能精准预测论文未来的生死。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1536\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1536\" data-height=\"864\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505181426\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4f48ab7d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKm6afB98W6UmESoYH4mXUc4pH142xiaia6lsYjDqzXV3UlTmkP1fntG7A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">ICML2023实验数据分析：在不同投稿数量下，蓝色柱状图（自评级校准分）的误差显著低于红色柱状图（评审员原始分）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7704517704517705\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"819\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"1576\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKkwpg4bsiaZfa0FeVzodcy9QAUVHTPsUhBXkXuIxD91jOgkQwdmmiciamw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"819.9288256227759\" data-cropy1=\"637.7224199288255\" data-cropy2=\"1269.750889679715\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"433\" data-imgfileid=\"505181427\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0789c074&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKFGghqVY8vBgCic3RgMKPicptngd9YrTfwO0ogFxia01Ds9tQyMia7mqptA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">数据显示，作者自评排在第一位的论文，其16个月后的引用量，是末位论文的200%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">很多时候，评审员因为看不懂，把真正的神作杀掉了；而作者心里门儿清——「这篇是灌水的，那篇才是改变世界的」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这不只是一次规则调整，这是对「同行评审神圣性」的祛魅。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">官方终于承认：在这个信息过载的时代，与其相信一个只读了你论文20分钟的陌生人，不如利用作者想「赢」的野心，引导他说出真话。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">图灵奖得主「叛变」：客观已死，偏见万岁</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这张牌之所以能打出来，是因为桌子对面坐着一位真正的「神」——Yoshua Bengio</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1536\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1536\" data-height=\"1024\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" data-imgfileid=\"505181428\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b11fd4e7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicK2Gte9bO90wiaBOuEkLvRJQejUnCicOtPpVOQSu7kvzvE0rbeXQ4raM5w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在JASA的官方讨论稿中，Bengio并没有把这看作一次简单的规则修补，他将其定义为：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">机器学习与统计学的一次强力协同（PowerfulSynergy）。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 24px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.38625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1600\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"618\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"217\" data-imgfileid=\"505181429\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cf2b6b52&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKk2aeGicsEXFvpAVSLrebiaPvbBbavO8tQ1e5tjKXtK1tdy9JYQu7wmXA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">不同博弈策略下的误差缩减。通过「保序机制」，均方误差的改善幅度最高达23.48%</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为什么连AI教父都「叛变」了？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在传统的科学理想国里，我们迷信「客观」。我们认为评审员是公正的法官，作者是狡猾的辩护人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但在Bengio看来，这种洁癖在30000篇投稿的噪音面前，不仅幼稚，而且低效。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Bengio及其合作者DinghuaiZhang在评论中指出了一个极其深刻的哲学转变：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">承认「噪音」统治：当评审系统因过载已退化为「随机数生成器」，盲目追求绝对客观，本质上是一种由于傲慢导致的低效。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">拥抱「主观」信号：既然作者是最了解论文的人，为什么要把这个「信噪比」最高的信息源屏蔽掉？</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">因此，所谓的「偏见」，只要经过统计学修正，就是最珍贵的「特征」。这不仅仅是分数的博弈，更是「慢科学」的回归。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"768\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"768\" data-height=\"512\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" data-imgfileid=\"505181430\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c3c92da4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKhiajxHBDUToOr5BicmyVYjRZegEDD5l0wjl0x2kAJqibay1wTL5KBhoqA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你以为Bengio只是支持一种打分算法吗？不。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">作为长期呼吁抵制「PublishorPerish（不发表就出局）」的领军人物，Bengio看重的是这个机制背后的「自省」功能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他甚至在评论中提出了更激进的「多维降维」构想：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">未来的作者不应该只排「好坏」，而应该被要求在多个维度上自首：</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"font-style:normal;\">\n     <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-style: normal;\">这篇论文是新颖但粗糙的吗？</span></span></em></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"font-style:normal;\">\n     <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-style: normal;\">还是严谨但老套的？</span></span></em></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是一种对学术浮躁风气的技术性矫正。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当作者被迫对自己的三篇论文进行排序时，他必须在深夜里扪心自问：「难道我真的在灌水？」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种「强制性内省」，或许才是Bengio眼中，比筛选论文更重要的价值。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">算法折叠：豪门疯狂套利，散户只配「裸奔」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">如果你看到这里觉得：「太好了，终于有人来整治乱打分的评审了！」</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">先别急着庆祝。请先看一眼你手中的筹码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这项看似完美的「博弈论神技」，其实隐藏着一个被默许的「贫富准入门槛」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">「自评级机制」生效的前提，是你必须至少投两篇论文。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你得先有PaperA和PaperB，系统才能通过A&gt;B的逻辑来校准分数。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果你只投了一篇呢？对不起，系统救不了你。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你依然只能在那个充满了AI垃圾评论、随机打分的旧系统里裸奔。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是一场针对「学术散户」的精准降维打击。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"800\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"450\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505181431\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=71c31784&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKMFfAr4AgakUb1dGa7vOZ29hWpGY4MqMYk2Ash6Nm93bOiaviaWttzmMQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据ICML2023的官方统计数据显示，75.5%的作者，只投了一篇论文。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着那25%的「大户」，手里的多篇论文不再只是成果，而是变成了可以相互对冲、用来校准分数的「套利筹码」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们可以通过精妙的排序，利用统计学算法为自己的神作穿上「防弹衣」，挡住瞎眼评审的子弹。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22375\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1600\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"358\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"126\" data-imgfileid=\"505181432\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=370ea5e5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKypLakb7IItY0y02gOA3JoaSicqTxfBYEfpf9w3meGKYNKa8iaxljUDdQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">MSE缩减的置信区间。在99%的置信水平下，误差缩减依然保持在极高区间，</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而75%的「普通玩家」面对的，依然是「俄罗斯轮盘」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果遇到一个心情不好的评审员给了你3分，你没有任何数学工具可以反抗。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7752659574468085\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"752\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"1576\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKkwpg4bsiaZfa0FeVzodcy9QAUVHTPsUhBXkXuIxD91jOgkQwdmmiciamw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"825.6227758007118\" data-cropx2=\"1577.2241992882564\" data-cropy1=\"657.6512455516014\" data-cropy2=\"1241.2811387900354\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"436\" data-imgfileid=\"505181433\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=75bca8de&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKcDpiaZ7IT39xHtVFWsDYAxicPnxo7uNFR1Iv9bic0q5dLzvFAK75pBqeA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">筹码越多，护甲越厚。观察红蓝柱对比可见，作者投出的论文越多（横轴），利用自评级机制缩减误差（蓝色柱状图下降幅度）的空间往往越稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">香港大学的WeichenWang和LSE的ChengchunShi认为，这种机制实际上是在奖励「灌水」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了获得「被校准」的资格，为了获得那层算法保护壳，实验室会被迫把一项成果拆成三项（SalamiSlicing），凑足「自评级」的入场券。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">以前的强者靠质量通吃；以后的强者，恐将靠「堆量」和「排序策略」进行收割。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">ICML2026的新政，或许确实解决了「评审准确度」的问题，但它解决的方式是——优先保护那些拥有更多资源的人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是一次赤裸裸的「算法折叠」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">ICML2026砸碎的不仅是评审规则，还有我们对「学术乌托邦」的最后一点幻想。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当人类评审员在30000篇论文的洪流中彻底窒息，机器和算法接管裁判权，已是历史的必然。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这不再是一个比拼谁更「客观」的时代，这是一个比拼谁更懂「博弈」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">ICML已经用算法告诉我们，在算力爆炸的今天，「诚实」不再是一种高尚的道德自律，而是一条被博弈论强制执行的、冷冰冰的「生存策略」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">醒醒吧，旧世界已经塌了。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "ICML 2026 推出作者自评级新规以应对审稿危机，该机制利用博弈论校准作者自评排序，旨在筛选高质量论文，却可能导致学术资源两极分化，对学术“散户”构成挑战。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "ICML 2026 推出作者自评级新规以应对审稿危机，该机制利用博弈论校准作者自评排序，旨在筛选高质量论文，却可能导致学术资源两极分化，对学术“散户”构成挑战。",
  "summary": "NeurIPS 投稿量飙升至 3 万篇，导致传统同行评审系统濒临崩溃。为应对此危机，ICML 2026 提出颠覆性的“作者自评级”新政，鼓励作者对其投稿论文进行排序。该机制基于博弈论的“保序回归”原理，利用作者的排名顺序校准论文分数，旨在通过作者的“偏见”和“求胜心”更精准地识别高质量论文。图灵奖得主 Yoshua Bengio 对此表示支持，认为这是在信息过载时代，拥抱主观信号并进行统计学修正的“慢科学”回归，并提出多维度自评的激进构想。然而，该机制存在隐忧：它要求作者至少提交两篇论文才能生效，这意味着仅投稿一篇的“学术散户”无法获得算法保护，而“学术大户”则能利用多篇论文进行“套利”，获取算法优势。这可能导致实验室为获取资格而“灌水”，加剧学术资源两极分化，最终使得规则向有资源者倾斜，打破学术乌托邦幻想。",
